
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Classes";
}

<!-- ***** Our Classes Start ***** -->
    <section class="section" id="our-classes">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3">
                    <div class="section-heading">
                        <h2>Our <em>Classes</em></h2>
                        <img src="~/assets/images/line-dec.png" alt="">
                        <p>The site provides you with variations of classes in different categories.they are fun way to lose weight and get in shape fast. You can start your journey now</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row" id="tabs">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href='#tabs-1'><img src="~/assets/images/tabs-first-icon.png" alt="">Weight lifting Class</a></li>
                        <li><a href='#tabs-2'><img src="~/assets/images/tabs-first-icon.png" alt="">Cardio Class</a></li>
                        <li><a href='#tabs-3'><img src="~/assets/images/tabs-first-icon.png" alt="">Fitness Class</a></li>
                        <li><a href='#tabs-4'><img src="~/assets/images/tabs-first-icon.png" alt="">Yoga Class</a></li>
                    <div class="main-rounded-button"><a href="#schedule">View All Schedules</a></div>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                <section class='tabs-content'>
                    <article id='tabs-1'>
                        <img src="~/assets/images/training-image-01.jpg" alt="First Class">
                        <h4>Weight lifting Class</h4>
                        <p>Weight lifting is a type of strength training that involves lifting and lowering weights, such as barbells, dumbbells, or kettlebells. Weight lifting can help improve muscle mass, strength, endurance, and power. Weight lifting can also benefit your health by reducing the risk of chronic diseases, such as diabetes, heart disease, and osteoporosis.</p>
                        <div class="main-button">
                            <a href="#schedule">View Schedule</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article id='tabs-2'>
                        <img src="~/assets/images/training-image-02.jpg" alt="Second Training">
                        <h4>Cardio Class</h4>
                        <p>Cardio Sport is a comprehensive training system that will get you into the best shape of your life.This unique method is designed to excite and inspire people who love team sports (and music). The technical definition of Cardio Sport is comprehensive athletic conditioning integration.</p>
                        <div class="main-button">
                            <a href="#schedule">View Schedule</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article id='tabs-3'>
                        <img src="~/assets/images/training-image-03.jpg" alt="Third Class">
                        <h4>Fitness Class</h4>
                        <p>Physical fitness is a state of health and well-being and, more specifically, the ability to perform aspects of sports, occupations and daily activities. Physical fitness is generally achieved through proper nutrition, moderate-vigorous physical exercise, and sufficient rest along with a formal recovery plan.</p>
                        <div class="main-button">
                            <a href="#schedule">View Schedule</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article id='tabs-4'>
                        <img src="~/assets/images/training-image-04.jpg" alt="Fourth Training">
                        <h4>Yoga Class</h4>
                        <p>Yoga is an ancient practice that involves physical poses, concentration, and deep breathing. Yoga aims to promote physical and mental well-being and spiritual connection. There are several types of yoga and each one has its own characteristics.</p>
                        <div class="main-button">
                            <a href="#schedule">View Schedule</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ***** Our Classes End ***** -->
    
